1. **Register a Circles Profile** 

1) To interact with the Protocol and create a Circles Account, you are required to first register a profile (“**Circles Profile**”). In order to do so, you must register a unique username through the App, which will be linked to the Safe wallet you designate as your Circles Account. Your username is a mandatory requirement for registering your Circles Profile and interacting with the Protocol. 

